data.meta_description:
32 likes, 1 comments - drummmrhythmicevents on June 27, 2021: "From yesterday in #Pacifica: 

“This “drummm” lesson and circle went far beyond my expectations! Thank you, Jeni Swerdlow for making it so. I had a ball!”

The truth is, we all had a ball. Perhaps me most of all. Despite the traffic... and the fog... and my malfunctioning roller cart. 

It was a beautiful day to connect with new people, let go of stress, and celebrate all the things.

Don’t worry if you missed it. I’ll be back next month!
